<specimenCount id="7AC088895E5DC512FC63BBABFB9EE9A4" box="[923,1096,1207,1231]" pageId="95" pageNumber="96" type="generic">two specimens</specimenCount>
originally described and an additional specimen listed here.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
